 |\n| GET /api/clips/:name | Range拖拽 |\n| GET /api/events | 事件列表 |\n| GET /api/storage | 存储信息 |\n| GET /api/settings | 获取设置 |\n| POST /api/settings | 更新设置 |\n| WS /api/ws/signal | WebRTC信令 |\n\n## 配置\n\n配置文件: `config.yaml`\n\n```yaml\nserver:\n  port: 8080\n\nstorage:\n  max_gb: 50\n  clip_dir: ./clips\n\ncapture:\n  device: 0\n  width: 640\n  height: 480\n  fps: 25\n\nencoding:\n  record_bitrate: 4000000  # 4Mbps\n  monitor_bitrate: 500000   # 500kbps\n  segment_min: 5\n\ndetection:\n  enabled: true\n  socket: /tmp/visionloop_det.sock\n  detect_fall: true\n  detect_cry: true\n  detect_noise: true\n  detect_intruder: true\n  sensitivity: 0.7\n```\n\n## 性能\n\n| 指标 | 目标 |\n|------|------|\n| 监看延迟 | < 1秒 |\n| 编码CPU | < 5% (硬编码) |\n| 存储GC | 自动清理 |\n| 启动时间 | < 5秒 |\n\n## 技术栈\n\n- **Go**: gocv, Pion WebRTC, Gin\n- **FFmpeg**: H.264/H.265硬编码\n- **Python**: YOLOv8, onnxruntime, librosa\n- **Vue3**: Vite, Pinia, video.js\n- **ML**: YOLOv8-pose, YOLOv8-face\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
