{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_d7zyekq3mt23_2","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# VisionLoop - 智能监控循环录制系统\n     2→\n     3→版本 1.0.0 | 2026-03-25\n     4→\n     5→## 特性\n     6→\n     7→- **实时监看**: WebRTC低延迟推送，延迟<1秒\n     8→- **循环录制**: MP4分段录制，自动GC清理\n     9→- **事件检测**: YOLOv8姿态/哭声/异响/陌生人检测\n    10→- **历史回放**: Range请求拖拽，事件时间轴标注\n    11→- **开箱即用**: 双击运行，浏览器访问\n    12→\n    13→## 系统要求\n    14→\n    15→- Windows 10/11 (x64)\n    16→- Go 1.21+\n    17→- Python 3.9+ (用于检测进程)\n    18→- FFmpeg (可选，用于硬编码)\n    19→\n    20→## 快速开始\n    21→\n    22→### 1. 构建\n    23→\n    24→```bash\n    25→# 安装Go依赖\n    26→go mod download\n    27→\n    28→# 构建主程序\n    29→go build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o VisionLoop.exe ./cmd/server\n    30→\n    31→# 构建前端 (需要Node.js)\n    32→cd web && npm install && npm run build && cd ..\n    33→\n    34→# 构建检测进程 (需要Python)\n    35→cd detection && pip install -r requirements.txt && cd ..\n    36→```\n    37→\n    38→### 2. 运行\n    39→\n    40→```bash\n    41→# 启动主程序\n    42→./VisionLoop.exe\n    43→\n    44→# 启动检测进程 (独立终端)\n    45→cd detection && python main.py\n    46→```\n    47→\n    48→### 3. 访问\n    49→\n    50→打开浏览器访问 http://localhost:8080\n    51→\n    52→## 项目结构\n    53→\n    54→```\n    55→VisionLoop/\n    56→├── cmd/server/           # 主入口\n    57→├── internal/\n    58→│   ├── capture/          # gocv摄像头采集\n    59→│   ├── encoder/          # FFmpeg编码器\n    60→│   ├── mp4/              # MP4分段写入\n    61→│   ├── storage/          # 存储GC\n    62→│   ├── webrtc/           # Pion WebRTC\n    63→│   ├── ipc/              # Unix Socket IPC\n    64→│   └── api/              # Gin HTTP服务\n    65→├── web/                  # Vue3前端\n    66→│   ├── src/views/        # 页面组件\n    67→│   └── dist/             # 构建输出\n    68→├── detection/            # Python检测进程\n    69→│   ├── main.py           # 入口\n    70→│   ├── yolo.py           # YOLOv8检测\n    71→│   └── audio.py          # 音频检测\n    72→└── clips/                # 录像存储目录\n    73→```\n    74→\n    75→## API\n    76→\n    77→| 接口 | 说明 |\n    78→|------|------|\n    79→| GET / | Vue3 SPA |\n    80→| GET /api/clips | 录像列表 |\n    81→| GET /api/clips/:name | Range拖拽 |\n    82→| GET /api/events | 事件列表 |\n    83→| GET /api/storage | 存储信息 |\n    84→| GET /api/settings | 获取设置 |\n    85→| POST /api/settings | 更新设置 |\n    86→| WS /api/ws/signal | WebRTC信令 |\n    87→\n    88→## 配置\n    89→\n    90→配置文件: `config.yaml`\n    91→\n    92→```yaml\n    93→server:\n    94→  port: 8080\n    95→\n    96→storage:\n    97→  max_gb: 50\n    98→  clip_dir: ./clips\n    99→\n   100→capture:\n   101→  device: 0\n   102→  width: 640\n   103→  height: 480\n   104→  fps: 25\n   105→\n   106→encoding:\n   107→  record_bitrate: 4000000  # 4Mbps\n   108→  monitor_bitrate: 500000   # 500kbps\n   109→  segment_min: 5\n   110→\n   111→detection:\n   112→  enabled: true\n   113→  socket: /tmp/visionloop_det.sock\n   114→  detect_fall: true\n   115→  detect_cry: true\n   116→  detect_noise: true\n   117→  detect_intruder: true\n   118→  sensitivity: 0.7\n   119→```\n   120→\n   121→## 性能\n   122→\n   123→| 指标 | 目标 |\n   124→|------|------|\n   125→| 监看延迟 | < 1秒 |\n   126→| 编码CPU | < 5% (硬编码) |\n   127→| 存储GC | 自动清理 |\n   128→| 启动时间 | < 5秒 |\n   129→\n   130→## 技术栈\n   131→\n   132→- **Go**: gocv, Pion WebRTC, Gin\n   133→- **FFmpeg**: H.264/H.265硬编码\n   134→- **Python**: YOLOv8, onnxruntime, librosa\n   135→- **Vue3**: Vite, Pinia, video.js\n   136→- **ML**: YOLOv8-pose, YOLOv8-face\n   137→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a9d5d52f-eaa4-4eb7-9183-48d13a46d113","uuid":"f2bd3312-c041-4016-a28a-a4db22c7e56b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T12:33:46.155Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/app/data/autodev/VisionLoop-----100--2026-03-2-1774439980/README.md","content":"# VisionLoop - 智能监控循环录制系统\n\n版本 1.0.0 | 2026-03-25\n\n## 特性\n\n- **实时监看**: WebRTC低延迟推送，延迟<1秒\n- **循环录制**: MP4分段录制，自动GC清理\n- **事件检测**: YOLOv8姿态/哭声/异响/陌生人检测\n- **历史回放**: Range请求拖拽，事件时间轴标注\n- **开箱即用**: 双击运行，浏览器访问\n\n## 系统要求\n\n- Windows 10/11 (x64)\n- Go 1.21+\n- Python 3.9+ (用于检测进程)\n- FFmpeg (可选，用于硬编码)\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 构建\n\n```bash\n# 安装Go依赖\ngo mod download\n\n# 构建主程序\ngo build -ldflags=\"-s -w\" -o VisionLoop.exe ./cmd/server\n\n# 构建前端 (需要Node.js)\ncd web && npm install && npm run build && cd ..\n\n# 构建检测进程 (需要Python)\ncd detection && pip install -r requirements.txt && cd ..\n```\n\n### 2. 运行\n\n```bash\n# 启动主程序\n./VisionLoop.exe\n\n# 启动检测进程 (独立终端)\ncd detection && python main.py\n```\n\n### 3. 访问\n\n打开浏览器访问 http://localhost:8080\n\n## 项目结构\n\n```\nVisionLoop/\n├── cmd/server/           # 主入口\n├── internal/\n│   ├── capture/          # gocv摄像头采集\n│   ├── encoder/          # FFmpeg编码器\n│   ├── mp4/              # MP4分段写入\n│   ├── storage/          # 存储GC\n│   ├── webrtc/           # Pion WebRTC\n│   ├── ipc/              # Unix Socket IPC\n│   └── api/              # Gin HTTP服务\n├── web/                  # Vue3前端\n│   ├── src/views/        # 页面组件\n│   └── dist/             # 构建输出\n├── detection/            # Python检测进程\n│   ├── main.py           # 入口\n│   ├── yolo.py           # YOLOv8检测\n│   └── audio.py          # 音频检测\n└── clips/                # 录像存储目录\n```\n\n## API\n\n| 接口 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| GET / | Vue3 SPA |\n| GET /api/clips | 录像列表 |\n| GET /api/clips/:name | Range拖拽 |\n| GET /api/events | 事件列表 |\n| GET /api/storage | 存储信息 |\n| GET /api/settings | 获取设置 |\n| POST /api/settings | 更新设置 |\n| WS /api/ws/signal | WebRTC信令 |\n\n## 配置\n\n配置文件: `config.yaml`\n\n```yaml\nserver:\n  port: 8080\n\nstorage:\n  max_gb: 50\n  clip_dir: ./clips\n\ncapture:\n  device: 0\n  width: 640\n  height: 480\n  fps: 25\n\nencoding:\n  record_bitrate: 4000000  # 4Mbps\n  monitor_bitrate: 500000   # 500kbps\n  segment_min: 5\n\ndetection:\n  enabled: true\n  socket: /tmp/visionloop_det.sock\n  detect_fall: true\n  detect_cry: true\n  detect_noise: true\n  detect_intruder: true\n  sensitivity: 0.7\n```\n\n## 性能\n\n| 指标 | 目标 |\n|------|------|\n| 监看延迟 | < 1秒 |\n| 编码CPU | < 5% (硬编码) |\n| 存储GC | 自动清理 |\n| 启动时间 | < 5秒 |\n\n## 技术栈\n\n- **Go**: gocv, Pion WebRTC, Gin\n- **FFmpeg**: H.264/H.265硬编码\n- **Python**: YOLOv8, onnxruntime, librosa\n- **Vue3**: Vite, Pinia, video.js\n- **ML**: YOLOv8-pose, YOLOv8-face\n","numLines":137,"startLine":1,"totalLines":137}}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_d7zyekq3mt23_1","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package main\n     2→\n     3→import (\n     4→\t\"context\"\n     5→\t\"fmt\"\n     6→\t\"log\"\n     7→\t\"net/http\"\n     8→\t\"os\"\n     9→\t\"os/signal\"\n    10→\t\"path/filepath\"\n    11→\t\"syscall\"\n    12→\t\"time\"\n    13→\n    14→\t\"visionloop/internal/api\"\n    15→\t\"visionloop/internal/capture\"\n    16→\t\"visionloop/internal/encoder\"\n    17→\t\"visionloop/internal/ipc\"\n    18→\t\"visionloop/internal/mp4\"\n    19→\t\"visionloop/internal/storage\"\n    20→\t\"visionloop/internal/webrtc\"\n    21→)\n    22→\n    23→var (\n    24→\tVersion   = \"1.0.0\"\n    25→\tBuildTime = time.Now().Format(\"2006-01-02\")\n    26→)\n    27→\n    28→func main() {\n    29→\tlog.SetFlags(log.LstdFlags | log.Lshortfile)\n    30→\tlog.Printf(\"VisionLoop v%s (built: %s) starting...\", Version, BuildTime)\n    31→\n    32→\t// 工作目录\n    33→\tworkDir, err := os.Getwd()\n    34→\tif err != nil {\n    35→\t\tlog.Fatal(\"get workdir failed:\", err)\n    36→\t}\n    37→\n    38→\t// 确保必要目录存在\n    39→\tclipsDir := filepath.Join(workDir, \"clips\")\n    40→\tos.MkdirAll(clipsDir, 0755)\n    41→\tos.MkdirAll(filepath.Join(workDir, \"events\"), 0755)\n    42→\tos.MkdirAll(filepath.Join(workDir, \"screenshots\"), 0755)\n    43→\n    44→\t// 配置\n    45→\tcfg := &Config{\n    46→\t\tClipsDir:     clipsDir,\n    47→\t\tEventsDir:    filepath.Join(workDir, \"events\"),\n    48→\t\tScreenshots:  filepath.Join(workDir, \"screenshots\"),\n    49→\t\tMaxStorageGB: 50.0,\n    50→\t\tSegmentMin:   5, // 5分钟分段\n    51→\t\tRecordBitrate: 4 * 1024 * 1024,  // 4Mbps\n    52→\t\tMonitorBitrate: 500 * 1024,       // 500kbps\n    53→\t}\n    54→\n    55→\t// 初始化存储GC\n    56→\tgc := storage.NewGC(cfg.ClipsDir, cfg.MaxStorageGB)\n    57→\n    58→\t// 初始化采集\n    59→\tcam, err := capture.NewCapture(0) // 默认摄像头\n    60→\tif err != nil {\n    61→\t\tlog.Printf(\"WARNING: camera init failed: %v, using test pattern\", err)\n    62→\t\tcam = capture.NewTestPattern(640, 480, 25)\n    63→\t}\n    64→\n    65→\t// 初始化编码器\n    66→\tenc, err := encoder.NewEncoder(encoder.EncoderConfig{\n    67→\t\tWidth:          640,\n    68→\t\tHeight:         480,\n    69→\t\tRecordBitrate:  cfg.RecordBitrate,\n    70→\t\tMonitorBitrate: cfg.MonitorBitrate,\n    71→\t\tFramerate:      25,\n    72→\t})\n    73→\tif err != nil {\n    74→\t\tlog.Fatal(\"encoder init failed:\", err)\n    75→\t}\n    76→\tdefer enc.Close()\n    77→\n    78→\t// 初始化MP4录制\n    79→\tmp4Writer, err := mp4.NewMP4Writer(cfg.ClipsDir, cfg.SegmentMin, enc.Width(), enc.Height(), cfg.RecordBitrate)\n    80→\tif err != nil {\n    81→\t\tlog.Fatal(\"mp4 writer init failed:\", err)\n    82→\t}\n    83→\tdefer mp4Writer.Close()\n    84→\n    85→\t// 初始化WebRTC\n    86→\twrtc := webrtc.NewWebRTC(enc.Width(), enc.Height())\n    87→\tdefer wrtc.Close()\n    88→\n    89→\t// 初始化Unix Socket IPC\n    90→\tsocketPath := \"/tmp/visionloop_det.sock\"\n    91→\tdetIPC, err := ipc.NewDetectionIPC(socketPath)\n    92→\tif err != nil {\n    93→\t\tlog.Printf(\"WARNING: detection IPC init failed: %v\", err)\n    94→\t} else {\n    95→\t\tdefer detIPC.Close()\n    96→\t}\n    97→\n    98→\t// 启动采集+编码+录制主循环\n    99→\tctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n   100→\tdefer cancel()\n   101→\n   102→\t// 采集通道（无缓冲，下游满则丢帧）\n   103→\tframeCh := make(chan *capture.Frame)\n   104→\n   105→\t// 启动采集goroutine\n   106→\tgo cam.CaptureLoop(ctx, frameCh)\n   107→\n   108→\t// 编码+录制goroutine\n   109→\tgo runEncodeLoop(ctx, frameCh, enc, mp4Writer, wrtc, detIPC, gc)\n   110→\n   111→\t// 初始化API服务\n   112→\tserver := api.NewServer(api.ServerConfig{\n   113→\t\tClipsDir:     cfg.ClipsDir,\n   114→\t\tEventsDir:    cfg.EventsDir,\n   115→\t\tScreenshots:  cfg.Screenshots,\n   116→\t\tMaxStorageGB: cfg.MaxStorageGB,\n   117→\t\tWebRTC:       wrtc,\n   118→\t\tVersion:      Version,\n   119→\t})\n